when I'm there, I really miss you.
<SYNC Start=288482><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=290256><P Class=ENCC>
So..
<SYNC Start=292486><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=293092><P Class=ENCC>
do you want to move in together?
<SYNC Start=295890><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=296596><P Class=ENCC>
Wow, Mike Hanigan..
<SYNC Start=299064><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
