<SYNC Start=435695><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=436636><P Class=ENCC>
Anyway, are you going to get<br>
a handyman to install this stuff?
<SYNC Start=440504><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
