right down the street?
<SYNC Start=472996><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=475541><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, you guys?<br>
Okay, we've got great news.
<SYNC Start=478738><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=478911><P Class=ENCC>
- Phoebe and I are moving in together.<br>
- Congratulations.
<SYNC Start=482347><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=482515><P Class=ENCC>
I know, it's so exciting. You know,<br>
I've never lived with a guy before.
<SYNC Start=486042><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486252><P Class=ENCC>
Well, it's just like living with a girl,<br>
