<SYNC Start=647813><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=648147><P Class=ENCC>
- Yeah, I know.<br>
- What? What do you mean, you "know"?
<SYNC Start=651583><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
